<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="transparent-adj">transparent <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /træns'pærənt/    美 /træns'pærənt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>透明的</strong></h4>
<h4 id="2-obvious">2.<strong>显而易见的 (obvious)；易懂的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a transparent lie 
明显的谎言</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>The state-run company is required to make its accounts as <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ as possible for its staff to monitor the use of money.   （2011 湖北改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. transparent / clear  </p></div>